pricing to consistent availability to safe transportation and storage arch is the most diversified american coal company providing customers with maximum sourcing flexibility proven resource with nearly  of the globe’s proven and probable reserves the united states has the most plentiful coal deposits in the world plentiful coal supplies translate into lower fuel prices for power generation and ultimately to lower electric bills for families and businesses on average americans pay  per kilowatthour whereas japanese and italians pay double that electricity rate arch is the second largest us coal reserve holder with a coal reserve base of more than  billion tons crude steel global steel production is dependent on coal metallurgical grade coal is a vital ingredient in twothirds of global steel production each year the united states already plays a sizable and increasingly essential role in global metallurgical coal markets as the world’s second largest exporter of coking coal growing demand for metallurgical coal coupled with scarcity of supply create a premium in the marketplace for highquality met coals arch plans to significantly grow metallurgical coal volumes to capitalize on the global steel boom steel production world crude steel production has increased  since  and demand continues to grow robustly the world steel association projects that steel consumption will climb by more than  by  that’s where coking and pci coals come in the largest steel producing countries – china japan india usa and russia – rely heavily and increasingly on metallurgical coal from the united states coal is vital to nearly  of the world’s steel production archs new leer mine is a worldclass metallurgical coal mining complex that supplies premium quality coking coal to steel makers steel use nations are urbanizing rapidly and building factories railroads power plants bridges and office buildings in the process this infrastructure needs steel and lots of it steel use worldwide increased nearly  between  and  china increased steel use over  during the same year time span because coal is a vital ingredient in the steelmaking process growth in steel demand translates to growth in metallurgical coal demand arch is among the worlds top  metallurgical coal suppliers strong essential driven arch coal nyse arch is a leading natural resource company we produce highquality metallurgical and thermal coal used to manufacture steel and generate electricity through our strong operating portfolio we are uniquely positioned to supply safe responsible and essential resources to these two distinct markets   to learn more about the new arch coal and hear from our chief executive officer john w eaves please visit the arch coal  online annual report   learn more about us  copyright  arch coal inc privacy terms site map arch coal inc  careers about our mines safety our vision awards careers history future news investors contact us eventspresentations faq sec filings stock information customers our customers our mines transportation our products environment how we mine reclamation energy future get the facts after mining awards news news releases awards media contact privacy policy copyright policy powered by coal video community community outreach education employment foundation contact careers search careers career search careers if your career is built around hard work and dedication and if youre seeking a company with a culture based on opportunity and autonomy  wed like to invite you to explore career opportunities with arch coal at arch coal you would be a part of one of the largest coal producers in the us we have employees in eight states including our corporate headquarters in st louis we employ approximately  hardworking individuals across the us in a variety of jobs from accountants to machine operators to environmental engineers we strive to be the employer of choice from our great benefits package to our focus on training for career enhancement because our su